These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, orange
City: prague, hamburg
1. the person traveling to prague is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to hamburg is the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Food   | orange | nectarine |
| City     | hamburg    | prague   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, aconite
House: colonial, craftsman
1. the colonial house is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Flower   | aconite | marigold        |
| House      | colonial  | craftsman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
