The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, comedy
1. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| City   | hannover    | rome |
| Movie-Genre   | action | comedy |

