.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
2 different pets are kept: goat, bird
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, marigold
1. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | goat      | bird |
| Flower       | aconite | marigold    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, chess
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, blue
1. the person who likes orange is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Hobby           | dancing | chess |
| Color   | blue    | orange         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, montecristo
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, january
1. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Cigar       | montecristo | tiparillo  |
| Birthday   | january  | march |

 #################################

 
