.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-11::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, subway
House: modern, townhouse
1. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
2. the modern house is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Transport   | subway | jet-ski   |
| House         | modern | townhouse |

